    <script>
     function toogleDropdown(dropdown) {
  let items;
   if(dropdown == 'menu'){
     items = document.querySelector("#mobile-hamburger-items");
   } else if(dropdown == 'submenu'){
     items = document.querySelector("#mobile-subdropdown");
   } else {
     items = document.querySelector("#mobile-subdropdown-2");
   } 
    if (items && items.matches('.hide')) {
        items.classList.remove('hide');
      } else if (items && !items.matches('.hide')) {
        items.classList.add('hide');
    }
}
  
function closeItem(){
  document.querySelector("#mobile-hamburger-items").classList.add('hide');
}
  
  /*Please do not remove this js - otherwise the slideshow only works if you manually scroll the page*/
  setTimeout(function(){
  window.scrollBy(0, 5); 
}, 500);
    </script>

    <script>
     var body_element = document.getElementsByTagName("BODY")[0]; 
  var allChannels =  JSON.parse(channelsJSON);
  function getChannelByZipcode(zipcode, isMobile, isTop) {
  
    document.querySelector(".change-location-div .found-station-list").innerText = "";
    //document.querySelector(".station-finder .found-station-list").innerText = "";
    var matchedChannels = [];
    var stationChannels = allChannels.Channels;
  
    for (var i = 0; i < stationChannels.length ; i++) {
      
      if(stationChannels[i].zip_code.includes(zipcode)) {
        console.log("testerer");
        var stationChannel = stationChannels[i];
        matchedChannels.push(stationChannel);
        
        document.querySelector("#station-img").style.display = "block";
        
        document.querySelector(".first-inner-wrapper").style.display = "block";
        document.querySelector(".second-inner-wrapper").style.display = "flex";
        document.querySelector(".no-shows-inner-wrapper").style.display = "none";
        document.querySelector(".mb-no-shows-inner-wrapper").style.display = "none";
        if(document.querySelector(".no-shows-inner-wrapper-mb")) {
        document.querySelector(".no-shows-inner-wrapper-mb").style.display = "none"; }
        
        document.querySelector("#station-img").src = matchedChannels[0].image;
        var stationCityText = "ON TV IN "+ matchedChannels[0].market_city +", "+matchedChannels[0].market_state;
        document.querySelector('.station-city').innerText = stationCityText;
        document.querySelector('.show-time').innerText = matchedChannels[0].affiliate +" "+ matchedChannels[0].station +", "+matchedChannels[0].time;
        createFoundStationDiv(stationChannel,isMobile, isTop);
      } 
     
    }

     
      if(matchedChannels.length == 0) {
        console.log("test");
        document.querySelector(".first-inner-wrapper").style.display = "none";
        document.querySelector(".second-inner-wrapper").style.display = "none";
        
        if (!isMobile && isTop == "topbar") {
    document.querySelector(".no-shows-inner-wrapper").style.display = "block";
        } else if(isTop == "topbar") {
        document.querySelector(".mb-no-shows-inner-wrapper").style.display = "block";
        } else if (isTop == "changeloc") {
        document.querySelector(".no-shows-inner-wrapper-mb").style.display = "block";
        }
        
        
      }
    
    var stationLoc = ""; 
    if (!isMobile && isTop == "topbar") {
       stationLoc = document.querySelector('.station-found-wrapper-top');
    } else if (!isMobile && isTop == "bar") {
       stationLoc = document.querySelector('.station-found-wrapper-bar');
    } 
      
    if (isTop == "changeloc") {
       document.querySelector('.station-input-inner').value = "";
    } else if(!isMobile) {
    stationLoc.appendChild(document.querySelector('.station-found-wrapper'));
    }
    
    if(isMobile) {
    document.querySelector('.station-found-wrapper .first-wrapper').style.display = "none";
    }

    if(!isMobile && isTop == 'topbar') {
       document.querySelector('.station-finder .watch').classList.add('watch-oz');
       document.querySelector('.station-finder .station-input').style.display = "none";
       document.querySelector('.station-finder .station-button').style.display = "none";
       document.querySelector('.station-text').style.display = "none";
      
       document.querySelector('.station-found-text').style.display = "block";
      if(document.querySelector('.find-our-station')) {
      	document.querySelector('.find-our-station').style.display = "flex";
      }
      document.querySelector('.station-input').value = "";
     } else if (isTop == 'bar') {
       document.querySelector('.station-finder .watch').classList.remove('watch-oz');
       document.querySelector('.station-finder .station-input').style.display = "inline-block";
       document.querySelector('.station-finder .station-button').style.display = "inline-block";
       document.querySelector('.station-text').style.display = "inline-block";
       document.querySelector('.station-found-text').style.display = "none";
       document.querySelector('.find-our-station').style.display = "none";
       document.querySelector('.station-input-bar').value = "";
     }
     document.querySelector('.station-found-wrapper').style.display = "block";
    
  }
  
  
  function toggleChangeLocation() {
  	var getCLDiv = document.querySelector('.change-location-div');
    if (getCLDiv.style.display == "inline-block") {
    	getCLDiv.style.display = "none";
    } else {
      getCLDiv.style.display = "inline-block";
    }
  }
  
  function closeFinder(class1, class2) {
     document.querySelector(class1).style.display = "none";      document.querySelector(class2).innerText = "";
  }
  
  function createFoundStationDiv(stationChannel,isMobile, isTop) {
    	var stationListWrap = document.createElement("div");
    	stationListWrap.classList.add("station-list-wrapper");

    	var stationImgWrap = document.createElement("div");
    	stationImgWrap.classList.add("station-img-wrapper");

    	var stationImg = document.createElement("img");
    	stationImg.classList.add("station-img");
    	stationImg.src = stationChannel.image;
    	stationImg.height = 60;
    	stationImg.width = 60;
    	stationImg.alt = "station-logo";

        stationImgWrap.appendChild(stationImg);
        stationListWrap.appendChild(stationImgWrap);

        var stationDetailsWrap = document.createElement("div");
    	stationDetailsWrap.classList.add("station-detail-wrapper");

    	var stationCity = document.createElement("span");
    	stationCity.classList.add("station-city");
        stationCity.innerText = stationChannel.affiliate + " " + stationChannel.station;

    	var showTime = document.createElement("span");
    	showTime.classList.add("show-time");
    	showTime.innerText = stationChannel.time;
        
        stationDetailsWrap.appendChild(stationCity);
        stationDetailsWrap.appendChild(showTime);

        stationListWrap.appendChild(stationDetailsWrap);
        if (isMobile && isTop == "topbar") {
    document.querySelector(".mb-station-finder .found-station-list").appendChild(stationListWrap);
          document.querySelector('.station-finder-close').style.display = "flex";
    
    } else if (isMobile && isTop == "bar") {
    document.querySelector(".find-station .found-station-list").appendChild(stationListWrap);
      document.querySelector('.station-finder-close-bar').style.display = "flex";
    
    } else {
        document.querySelector(".change-location-div .found-station-list").appendChild(stationListWrap);
    }
}
    </script>

window.REBELMOUSE_TASKS_QUEUE.push(function(){

    
        function noop() {}

function queryParamsReducer(accum, queryPair) {
  var pieces = queryPair.split("=");
  accum[pieces[0]] = pieces[1];
  return accum;
}

function getVideoData(encodedIframe) {
  var dummy = document.createElement("div");
  dummy.innerHTML = encodedIframe;
  var iframe = dummy.querySelector("iframe");
  var queryParams = iframe.src.replace("&amp;", "&").split("/embed/?")[1];
  return queryParams.split("&").reduce(queryParamsReducer, {});
}

function getVideoDataFromDataset(dataset) {
  return {
    uplynk_video_id: dataset.videoId,
    uplynk_video_url: dataset.url,
  };
}

function ensurePlay(player, videoHolder) {
  return function onTimeout() {
    if (!player.paused) {
      return;
    }

    var playerElement = videoHolder.querySelector(".vjs-big-play-button");
    if (playerElement) {
      playerElement.click();
    } else {
      setTimeout(ensurePlay(player, videoHolder), 100);
    }
  };
}

function filterTags(filter) {
  return filter.substring(0, 4) === "tag-";
}

function cleanTags(tag) {
  return tag.split("tag-")[1];
}

function onLibLoad(placeholder, container, videoInfo) {
  return function onLibLoadHandler() {
    var videoHolder = document.createElement("div");
    videoHolder.classList.add(
      "theoplayer-container",
      "video-js",
      "theoplayer-skin",
      "vjs-fluid"
    );
    container.innerHTML = "";
    container.appendChild(videoHolder);
    container.style.display = "block";

    placeholder.remove();
    var player = new THEOplayer.Player(videoHolder, {
      libraryLocation:
        "//cdn.myth.theoplayer.com/79d150c1-b817-4ff2-933e-b97bb25e15b7/",
      ui: { width: "100%", height: "100%" },
    });
    
    player.videoTracks.addEventListener('addtrack', function(addTrackEvent) {
      var videoTrackQualities = addTrackEvent.track.qualities;
      var index = -1;
      var maxHeight = 0;

      for(var i = 0; i < videoTrackQualities.length; i++){
        var track = videoTrackQualities[i];
        if(track.height > maxHeight){
          maxHeight = track.height;
          index = i;
        }
      }

      if(index >= 0){
        player.videoTracks[0].targetQuality = player.videoTracks[0].qualities[index];
      }
  
      setTimeout(ensurePlay(player, videoHolder), 100);
    });

    var now = parseInt(Date.now(), 10);
    var article = container.closest("article");
    var category =
      window.REBELMOUSE_THEOPLAYER_SECTION ||
      article.dataset.category ||
      article.parentNode.dataset.category;
    var tags = article.parentNode.className
      .split(" ")
      .filter(filterTags)
      .map(cleanTags)
      .join(",");
    var pubads =
      "https://pubads.g.doubleclick.net/gampad/ads?iu=/22204508100/oz_video&description_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.doctoroz.com%2F&tfcd=0&npa=0&sz=640x480&cust_params=video_id%3D" +
      videoInfo.uplynk_video_id +
      "%26sneaky%3D" +
      tags +
      "%26gtag%3D" +
      category +
      "&gdfp_req=1&output=vast&ad_rule=1&unviewed_position_start=1&env=vp&impl=s&correlator=" +
      now;

    player.source = {
      sources: {
        id: [videoInfo.uplynk_video_id],
        integration: "verizon-media",
      },
      ads: [
        {
          sources: pubads,
          integration: "google-ima",
        },
      ],
    };

    player.preload = "auto";
  };
}

function onIma3Load(placeholder, container, videoInfo) {
  return function onIma3LoadHandler() {
    window.REBELMOUSE_STDLIB.loadExternalScript(
      "https://cdn.myth.theoplayer.com/79d150c1-b817-4ff2-933e-b97bb25e15b7/THEOplayer.js",
      onLibLoad(placeholder, container, videoInfo)
    );
  };
}

function loadEmbed(placeholder, container, videoInfo) {
  window.REBELMOUSE_STDLIB.loadExternalScript(
    "https://imasdk.googleapis.com/js/sdkloader/ima3.js",
    onIma3Load(placeholder, container, videoInfo)
  );
  window.REBELMOUSE_STDLIB.loadExternalStylesheet(
    "https://cdn.myth.theoplayer.com/79d150c1-b817-4ff2-933e-b97bb25e15b7/ui.css",
    noop
  );
}

function onVideoClick(element) {
  return function onVideoClickHandler(event) {
    event.preventDefault();
    event.stopPropagation();

    var widgetHead = element.closest(".widget__head");
    var widgetPlaceholder, widgetVideo, videoInfo;
    if (widgetHead) {
      widgetPlaceholder = widgetHead.querySelector(".widget__image");
      widgetVideo = widgetHead.querySelector(".widget__video");
      var videoIframe = widgetHead.querySelector(
        'script[type="video-content"]'
      );
      videoInfo = getVideoData(videoIframe.innerText);
    } else {
      var uplynkContainer = element.closest(".uplynk-container");
      widgetVideo = document.createElement("div");
      widgetVideo.classList.add("widget__img--tag");
      videoInfo = getVideoDataFromDataset(uplynkContainer.dataset);
      widgetPlaceholder = document.createElement("div");
      var parent = uplynkContainer.parentNode;
      uplynkContainer.remove();
      parent.appendChild(widgetVideo);
    }
    loadEmbed(widgetPlaceholder, widgetVideo, videoInfo);
    return false;
  };
}

function onLazyVideo(element) {
  var copy = element.cloneNode(true);
  var parentNode = element.parentNode;
  var sibling = element.nextSibling;
  element.remove();
  parentNode.insertBefore(copy, sibling);

  copy.classList.remove("js-show-video");
  copy.classList.add("js-show-video-safe");
  copy.addEventListener("click", onVideoClick(copy), { captrue: true });
}

if ("createElementChangeListener" in window.REBELMOUSE_STDLIB) {
  window.REBELMOUSE_STDLIB.createElementChangeListener(
    ".widget__play.js-show-video",
    onLazyVideo
  );
} else {
  function ChangeListener(selector, callback) {
    var initializedNodes = new Set([]);

    function onEachNode(node) {
      if (!initializedNodes.has(node)) {
        callback(node);
        initializedNodes.add(node);
      }
    }

    function onDocumentMutation() {
      var nodes = document.querySelectorAll(selector);
      nodes.forEach(onEachNewNode);
    }

    var mutationObserver = new MutationObserver(onDocumentMutation);

    document.querySelectorAll(selector).forEach(onEachNode);
    mutationObserver.observe(document.body, { childList: true, subtree: true });
  }

  ChangeListener(".widget__play.js-show-video", onLazyVideo);
}
    

});

window.REBELMOUSE_TASKS_QUEUE.push(function(){

    
        setTimeout(function(){
//carrousel only loads after scroll, so here we are scrolling a little bit
  window.scrollBy(0, 5); 
  
  // remove headline from specific posts
  removeHeadlineAndLinks();
  removeTargetBlank();
  
  function removeHeadlineAndLinks(){
    debugger;
    let posts =  document.querySelectorAll(".featured-carousel .widget");
    for(let post of posts){
      if(post.querySelector(".custom-field-noheadline") && post.querySelector(".custom-field-noheadline").innerText == "True"){
        post.querySelector(".widget__body.clearfix").style.display = "none";
      } 
      
      if(post.querySelector(".custom-field-nolinkout") && post.querySelector(".custom-field-nolinkout").innerText == "True"){
        post.classList.add("headline-link-disabled");
      }  
      
    }
  }   
  
  //remove target blank
  function removeTargetBlank(){
    let posts =  document.querySelectorAll(".widget:not(.targed-removed)");
    
    for(let post of posts){
      if(post.querySelector("a.custom-post-headline")){
        post.querySelector("a.custom-post-headline").removeAttribute("target");
        post.classList.add("targed-removed");
      }  
    }
  }   
  
  
  
}, 200);
    

});

window.REBELMOUSE_TASKS_QUEUE.push(function(){

    
        document.querySelectorAll('.NC .widget .widget__image').forEach(function(i){i.setAttribute('style',i.getAttribute('style')+'background:url("'+i.getAttribute('data-runner-img-hd')+'");background-size:cover;background-position:center center;')});

var slides=document.querySelectorAll('.NC .widget');

function magicrotate(x,y){
var nc_cntr=parseInt(document.querySelector('.nc_cntr').value);nc_cntr=nc_cntr+1
if(y==1){nc_cntr=parseInt(x);document.querySelector('.nc_cntr').value=nc_cntr;}
if(nc_cntr==slides.length){nc_cntr=0}

slides.forEach(function(e){e.style.display='none';e.classList.remove('actz')});
document.querySelector('.NC .widget'+nc_cntr).style.display='block';document.querySelector('.NC .widget'+nc_cntr).classList.add('actz')

if(nc_cntr==0){document.querySelector('.nc_prev').setAttribute('data-value',(slides.length-1));}else{document.querySelector('.nc_prev').setAttribute('data-value',nc_cntr-1);}

if(nc_cntr==slides.length){document.querySelector('.nc_next').setAttribute('data-value',1);}else{document.querySelector('.nc_next').setAttribute('data-value',nc_cntr+1);}



document.querySelectorAll('.NC .nc_btns span').forEach(function(e){e.classList.remove('actz')});
document.querySelector('.NC .dot'+nc_cntr).classList.add('actz');
document.querySelector('.nc_cntr').value=nc_cntr;
}

setInterval(function(){var nc_cntr=parseInt(document.querySelector('.nc_cntr').value);console.log('Sliding to '+nc_cntr);magicrotate(nc_cntr,null)},3000);

function magicrotatebtn(x,y){
for(i=0; i<1000; i++){window.clearInterval(i);}magicrotate(x,y);document.querySelector('.nc_cntr').value=x;
setInterval(function(){var nc_cntr=parseInt(document.querySelector('.nc_cntr').value);console.log('Sliding to '+nc_cntr);magicrotate(nc_cntr,null)},3000);
}

document.querySelector('.nc_prev').setAttribute('data-value',slides.length-1);
document.querySelector('.nc_next').setAttribute('data-value',1);


document.querySelector('.nc_prev').addEventListener("click", function(e){var p=parseInt(document.querySelector('.nc_prev').getAttribute('data-value')); magicrotatebtn(p,1);});
document.querySelector('.nc_next').addEventListener("click", function(e){var n=parseInt(document.querySelector('.nc_next').getAttribute('data-value'));magicrotatebtn(n,1);});


document.querySelectorAll('.NC .widget').forEach(function(s,i){s.classList.add('widget'+i);document.querySelector('.nc_btns').insertAdjacentHTML('beforeend','<span class="dot'+i+'"></span>');document.querySelector('.dot'+i).addEventListener("click", function(){console.log(i);magicrotatebtn(i,1)})});document.querySelector('.dot0').classList.add('actz');
    

});
  </script>
